InsuranceContract.name: InsuranceContract
InsuranceContract.description: Represents insurance-specific contract information. Extension of Contract object, specifically for the insurance industry.

BrokerageAgencyId.description: The brokerage agency associated with the insurance contract.

BusinessLicenseId.description: Agency license associated with the insurance contract.

ContractId.description: The contract associated with the insurance contract.

EnrollmentCensusId.description: The enrollment group census associated with the insurance contract used during enrollment.

EnrollmentEndDate.description: The date when enrollment ends for the plans in the insurance contract.

EnrollmentStartDate.description: The date when enrollment starts for the plans in the insurance contract.

EnrollmentWaitingPeriod.description: The waiting period in days after joining date before enrollment can begin.

LastReferencedDate.description: The timestamp when the current user last accessed this record, a record related to this record, or a list view.

LastViewedDate.description: The timestamp when the current user last viewed this record or list view.

OwnerId.description: The owner associated with the insurance contract.

ProducerId.description: The producer or broker associated with the insurance contract.

UnderwriterId.description: The underwriter associated with the insurance contract.
